                    "description": "\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tThe Stack v2\n\t\n\n\n    \n\n\nThe dataset consists of 4 versions:\n\nbigcode/the-stack-v2: the full \"The Stack v2\" dataset \nbigcode/the-stack-v2-dedup: based on the bigcode/the-stack-v2 but further near-deduplicated\nbigcode/the-stack-v2-train-full-ids: based on the bigcode/the-stack-v2-dedup dataset but further filtered with heuristics and spanning 600+ programming languages. The data is grouped into repositories. <-- you are herebigcode/the-stack-v2-train-smol-ids: based on the\u2026 See the full description on the dataset page: https://huggingface.co/datasets/bigcode/the-stack-v2-train-full-ids.",
